        <h2 class="heading">Applyt for Accommodation at funai </h2>
        <ul class="section-txt">
            <li><strong>1. Does FUNAI Offer Hostel Accommodation for Freshmen?</strong> Yes, FUNAI provides hostel accommodation for freshmen. Spaces are allocated on a first-come, first-served basis, so early booking is essential.</li>
            
            <li><strong>2. How Much Is Hostel Accommodation at FUNAI?</strong> The cost of hostel accommodation at FUNAI ranges from ₦20,000 to ₦50,000 per academic session, depending on the type of hostel and facilities provided.</li>
            
            <li><strong>3. Campus Facilities at FUNAI for New Students:</strong> FUNAI offers a variety of campus facilities to enhance student life:
                <ul class="child-ul">
                    <li>Modern lecture halls and laboratories.</li>
                    <li>A well-equipped library.</li>
                    <li>Sports and recreational facilities.</li>
                    <li>Cafeterias and shopping centers.</li>
                    <li>Internet and IT support services.</li>
                    <li>Health services through the university clinic.</li>
                </ul>
            </li>
            
            <li><strong>4. How to Find Housing Near FUNAI:</strong> If you prefer off-campus housing, consider the following steps:
                <ul class="child-ul">
                    <li>Contact local estate agents in the Ndufu-Alike area.</li>
                    <li>Join student forums or groups for housing recommendations.</li>
                    <li>Visit neighborhoods near the university to inspect available rooms or apartments.</li>
                    <li>Ensure the location is safe and easily accessible.</li>
                </ul>
            </li>
            
            <li><strong>5. How to Book Hostel Space at FUNAI:</strong> To book a hostel space at FUNAI:
                <ul class="child-ul">
                    <li>Visit the <a href="https://portal.funai.edu.ng">FUNAI Hostel Portal</a>.</li>
                    <li>Log in with your student credentials.</li>
                    <li>Navigate to the accommodation section.</li>
                    <li>Select your preferred hostel and complete the payment.</li>
                    <li>Print the confirmation receipt for verification upon arrival.</li>
                </ul>
            </li>
        </ul>
